songs.title: I’m Good
songs.lyrics:

Ay, ay, ay
Hah, yeah, haheh, yeah
Hahah, ay, yeah
Yeah, yeah
Haha, oww!

[Hook: Pusha T & Pharrell]
You can find me in the streets, even in a drought
My mattress is full, why shouldn't I be out?
Hey buddy, I'm good (What they tell you?)
I'm good (What they tell you?)
I'm good (What she tell you?) I'm good (What you see?)
Two hundred dollar jeans with my favorite patch
Pullin' up my ride, hell yeah, my rims match
What they tell you?
I'm good (what they tell you?) I'm good (what they tell you?)
I'm good (what she tell you?) I'm good (what you see?)
I'm looking good

Man I'm killin' it ridin' in that brand new
(I'm looking good, I'm looking good, I'm looking good)
Swimmin' through the streets lookin' like I'm Shamu
(Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah)
In that big body, with the wet paint
I got some pocket change from selling wet weight
(I'm looking good)
Today is a good day, ice cubes on my chest
(I'm looking good, I'm looking good, I'm looking good)

(Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah)

(I'm looking good, I'm looking good, I'm looking good)
Hate it when you shinin' through the neighborhood
(Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah)
Brand new ride, niggas know the time
Hoes cut they eyes, we call them samurais
(I'm looking good)
(Whaaa!) Fly as I could ever be!
(I'm looking good, I'm looking good, I'm looking good)
A level of success that you could never see
(Yeah, yeah, yeah)
You jealous mane, we in propellers mane
Think about it, ain't shit you can tell us mane

I’m good (what she tell ya?) I’m good (what you see?)

Cruisin' on them 22's got me sittin' pretty

You should hear that engine purr, here kitty kitty
(Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah)
Ride through the city, e'erbody know me
And the sun is out, it's like it's shinin on me
(I'm looking good)
Shoutin out the homies as I breeze by
(I'm looking good, I'm looking good, I'm looking good)
I'm on cloud 9, and I ain't even high
(Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah)
Told my shorty I'll be back and I ain't even lie
Them VVSs be the best that money can buy
(I'm looking good)
I see you flirtin baby, them jeans is painted on her
(I'm looking good, I'm looking good, I'm looking good)
Mama lookin right, and I don't even want her
(Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah)
No need to take it personal but that's just how it be
No disrespect to you, I'm just enjoyin me (I'm looking good)
Finally I'm free, all my dues paid
(I'm looking good, I'm looking good, I'm looking good)
Them yellow diamonds got the charm like it's Minute Maid
(Yeah, yeah, yeah)
